parameters: I've obtained the 【\i[92]Book of Sacred Hearts】!
Minion A: "I can't stand it anymore! This job is so damn tedious!"
Minion A: "Hey, you got one on you?"
Minion A: "A cigarette, man! A cigarette!"

Minion B: "Just make sure you never smoke that in front of Lord
Itodrag, got it?"
Minion A: "What? Does he hate cigarettes or something...?"

Minion B: "No... it's not that... He seems to have a thing against
fire."
Minion A: "You're kidding, right? Even though he dresses like a cook?"

Minion B: "Because the guy who used fire in the kitchen got beaten
half to death..."
Minion A: "Oh, right... I'll be careful."
